r />\n嚇好喇唔好射中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83edf172319a438e1e14e0e2e5c002bd940919e","tid":2012094,"uid":97840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"呢個世界弱肉強食，盡量唔好打亂大自然法則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d52c6686f39995eb6f9b6751864d689c0e5f2a3","tid":2012094,"uid":134863,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d83edf172319a438e1e14e0e2e5c002bd940919e","tid":2012094,"uid":97840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"呢個世界弱肉強食，盡量唔好打亂大自然法則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"我就係大自然一部分"},{"pid":"2704016a2c34981ebc08e54541e0fd263b2ead0f","tid":2012094,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"點解佢哋又會俾你咁近影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840b44a3437f5d728ec33157f87b2e71c1b1c0a4","tid":2012094,"uid":101600,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"2704016a2c34981ebc08e54541e0fd263b2ead0f","tid":2012094,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"點解佢哋又會俾你咁近影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbi4QMK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffbi4QMK.png&h=1227aed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢哋老豆老母係到偷拍佢哋會扮定格<br />\n以為我哋睇佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常佢哋去搵食 偷偷地伸部手機拍照<br />\n佢哋返嚟見到我哋都唔會打我哋<br />\n企旁邊顆樹仔等我哋走 又會返去餵啲細<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdUWGVe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdUWGVe.jpg&h=e0c00d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放過木瓜 蘋果 燈 芒果佢哋都唔食<br />\n考慮買「剛脫皮的白色麵包蟲軟嫩」<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/redbulbul/照顧/照顧幼鳥\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Fredbulbul%2F%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%A7%2F%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%A7%E5%B9%BC%E9%B3%A5&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=4117d2a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/redbulbul/照顧/照顧幼鳥</a><br />\n<br />\n有四丶五年係我哋露台到玩啦<br />\n以前成日偷食我哋顆石榴樹仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ub6BGWq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fub6BGWq.jpg&h=2a429447&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61b8638c8ddea9d2cb1f9613f3392c4e749514c1","tid":2012094,"uid":33345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:14:33.000Z","msg":"我屋企一年都有幾次係呢隻雀嚟築巢<br />\n其實呢啲咩品種嚟？<br />\n老豆之前話燕子嚟築先係好嘢 之後拆咗個竇<br />\n不過最近幾次都無再拆"},{"pid":"59eeb33c0f7e4882c784a9951afde6bd1fb3de73","tid":2012094,"uid":103799,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d83edf172319a438e1e14e0e2e5c002bd940919e","tid":2012094,"uid":97840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"呢個世界弱肉強食，盡量唔好打亂大自然法則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:46:47.000Z","msg":"較弱嘅動物出現係你面前,你又有能力,呢個就係命中注定你要幫助佢幫助<br />\n<br />\n人發展到有側忍之心都係大自然嘅定律"}]}